<br>
Is that mind-blowingly scary or what? If they're not even prepared to go through the pregnancy to get a child - because they might end up 'fat' - are they really prepared for any other kind of hard work that comes with being a mother??  Hell, I don't have a maternal bone in my body, but that doesn't stop me from seeing that there is something very, very wrong with that picture.<br>
&lt;/all-new rant&gt;<br>
